<a href="https://iono.fm/e/643662">Content hosted by iono.fm</a> Top five Chivas Venture finalist Bernard Naudé of Aegis Environmental explains how his project protects the environment and provides businesses with an incentive to recycle their waste. The Chivas Venture competition gives away $1 million in no-strings funding, as well as expert coaching at the Chivas Venture Accelerator Programme, to social entrepreneurs who blend profit with purpose. The winner of the SA leg will be announced on January 23. Brought to you by Chivas Venture.